<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Conta de Admin Criada</title>
</head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f1f5f9;font-family:Segoe UI,Arial,sans-serif;color:#0f172a;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:#f1f5f9;padding:24px 12px;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center">
        <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width:640px;background:#ffffff;border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid #dbe4f0;">
          <tr>
            <td style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0f172a,#1d4ed8);padding:28px 24px;color:#ffffff;">
              <h1 style="margin:0;font-size:24px;line-height:1.3;">Bem-vindo(a), {{Name}}.</h1>
              <p style="margin:10px 0 0 0;font-size:14px;opacity:0.95;">Sua conta de administrador na Fiap Cloud Games foi criada com sucesso.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:24px;">
              <p style="margin:0 0 14px 0;font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;">
                Para o primeiro acesso, utilize a senha temporária abaixo:
              </p>
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="margin:0 0 16px 0;border:2px dashed #1d4ed8;border-radius:12px;background:#eff6ff;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="padding:18px 16px;text-align:center;">
                    <p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:1px;color:#1e3a8a;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;">Senha temporária</p>
                    <p style="margin:0;font-size:30px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:2px;color:#0b3aa4;word-break:break-all;">{{TemporaryPassword}}</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155;">
                Por segurança, altere essa senha imediatamente após o login.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding:16px 24px 24px 24px;">
              <p style="margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#64748b;line-height:1.5;">
                Se você não solicitou esta criação, entre em contato com o suporte.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
